.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, white, azure, orange, amber
There are 5 different nationalities: french, pakistani, brazilian, egyptian, mexican
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, davidoff, blend, tiparillo, swisher
There are 5 different favourite beverages: mirinda, iced-tea, sprite, fanta, almond-milk
5 different pets are kept: rat, snake, frog, cat, hamster

1. the french is the person who likes ebony
2. the pakistani is the owner of the rat
3. the person drinking mirinda is the person who likes white
4. the brazilian is the person drinking iced-tea
5. the person who likes white is to the right of the person who likes azure
6. the oliveros-smoker is the owner of the hamster
7. the davidoff-smoker is the person who likes orange
8. the person drinking sprite is in the middle
9. the egyptian is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the snake
11. the davidoff-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the cat
12. the tiparillo-smoker is the person drinking fanta
13. the mexican is the swisher-smoker
14. the egyptian is to the left or right of the person who likes amber

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   egyptian	|    brazilian	|     french	|    pakistani	|    mexican	|
| Color		|    orange	|      amber	|      ebony	|     azure	|     white	|
| Beverage	|     almond-milk	|      iced-tea	|      sprite	| fanta	|     mirinda	|
| Cigar		|     davidoff	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| tiparillo	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     snake	|     cat	|     hamster	|     rat	|     frog	|
